* Carnage was about to loose her temper and attack the raptor when a sudden 
flurry of activity burst around her and suddenly the other raptor was lifted 
into the air by, she couldn't believe it, a 10:2 Tarbosaurus!
She jumped back and shouted in surprise and disbelief as her attacker was 
being attacked...*

" Ahhh! Holy ...slagin son of a bitch!!!!"

* Carnage watched in horror as the huge tyrant tore into the other raptor's 
back and the raptor biting back, how...STUPID!!!
However stupid the raptors efforts were Carnage knew that this was no way 
for a being to die (even though Cyber Claw had attacked her)and jumped into 
the air, she landed onto the large dinosaur's shoulder and tore into it with 
no mercy!*
